text: Seán O'Connor (born 26 July 1937) is an Irish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Ireland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Belfast
